{"tid":1563223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"50,60,70後既巴絲打 可唔可以同我媽咪打打氣","createTime":"2019-09-12T10:27:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T11:16:24.000Z","uid":302655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8e334fee1a58fbeae6304e572dd1e8a451b54379","tid":1563223,"uid":302655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:27:04.000Z","msg":"其實小妹係90後 但係60後既媽咪竟然開始玩連登先過我<br />\n佢最近叫我幫佢推post 所以俾佢感染到自己都玩埋一份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係好欣賞佢有時仲會去參與集會<br />\n我地成日都會互share新聞 會睇白兵細良 <br />\n<br />\n但因為佢身邊好多朋友都係藍絲 尤其咩舊生會呀中學同學  個啲中佬上哂岸<br />\n媽咪間唔中就會同我慎係WhatsApp group chat因爲share新聞會俾人攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話識咗幾十年既朋友到而加先見到真面目<br />\n<br />\n我爸就藍到發黑 我就係澳洲讀緊書 所以我媽有時都幾孤立無援<br />\n所以小妹想藉此機會問問有無50,60,70後既人係到<br />\n話俾我媽知佢並不孤單<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPlz幫我推"},{"pid":"293857bd3c7658872caf801d8cc4dea6a24a0b64","tid":1563223,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:27:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"98f80c2c22c1814fef5f423ba700320b76e4f246","tid":1563223,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec